<i>noun</i>: 문구 [문꾸], 글귀 [글뀌], 구절 [구절], 구 [구] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>문구 [문꾸]</dt><br>
<dd>words; phrase</dd><br>
<dd>특정한 뜻을 나타내는, 몇 낱말로 된 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A sequence of several words that expresses a certain meaning.</dd><br>
<dt>글귀 [글뀌]</dt><br>
<dd>phrase</dd><br>
<dd>몇 글자 또는 몇 단어로 된 짧은 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A short writing that consists of several letters or words.</dd><br>
<dt>구절 [구절]</dt><br>
<dd>phrase</dd><br>
<dd>한 토막의 말이나 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A small part of a speech or piece of writing</dd><br>
<dt>구 [구]</dt><br>
<dd>1. phrase</dd><br>
<dd>둘 이상의 단어가 모여 문장의 일부분을 이루는 말의 단위.</dd><br>
<dd>The unit of speech that forms part of a sentence by combining two or more words.</dd><br>
<dd>2. line</dd><br>
<dd>시조나 사설에서 어절을 세는 단위가 되는 짧은 토막.</dd><br>
<dd>In traditional Korean three-verse poetry or narratives, a phrasal segment that serves as a unit for counting the number of syntactic words.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>